div.div: Saya is a seemingly normal girl living with her father in a shrine. During the day she goes to school and spends time with her friends at a local cafe. But when night falls Saya is called upon to protect her village from strange monsters. (Source: Anime News Network)

While working as a small supporting actor in a movie, Ki Man-Seong has nothing else going for him. However, that was when, through mysterious circumstances, the movie set had become reality during filming.
With the sound of the directors cut, during that short take, hes not an actor but actually thrown into the events occurring, showing the pain and emotions he faces at that moment.
He can only come back if he creates that perfect take! Can he grow to become the greatest actor?
(Source: Kakao, translated)
